# The only docker build is the sandbox runner (runner/Dockerfile), built
# from the repo root so it can vendor the benchhub package. Whitelist just
# what that build needs — everything else (uploads/, .git/, database.db,
# tests/, archive/, the venv) stays out of the build context.
*
!benchhub/
!runner/
# Keep cruft out even from the whitelisted dirs.
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
